Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在 再次見到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定又會撒嬌的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而無法前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的多摩川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲夏的花依然開放
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在707室等著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還做了同樣款式的浴衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再這樣閒逛 我可要先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶 有蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又黑又大 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書上有寫的 是很有名的蝴蝶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是黑鳳蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑鳳蝶？不是蝴蝶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫作黑鳳蝶的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑鳳蝶蝴蝶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟普通的蝴蝶有什麼不一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近和五月講話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會讓我想起以前的真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為那傢伙只有六歲兒童的程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們又說我什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要怎麼系？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要系和小八一樣的蝴蝶結
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是蝴蝶結 而是叫作花文庫的腰帶結
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是年輕女孩子系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小八也不可以系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（厚臉皮哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很煩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是一年一度的多摩川煙花大會的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論大家多麼忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這一天 一定會回到這間房子裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著同樣的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可以了 就這點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天就開始喝酒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到放煙花就醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 每次見到泰都是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像是活化石一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是隔了幾個月時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會變啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 泰從高中開始就完全沒變過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使活到一千歲 一定還是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸也沒什麼改變呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說身高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很囉嗦唉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸 要不要衝個澡 換上浴衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是沖澡 我要沐浴 幫我放水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 遵命 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮呢 今天不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放煙花之前會到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙還是那麼我行我素
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 五月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還穿著浴衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 伸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡這個古裝人偶系列了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是給你買的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 五月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快謝謝叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時光的流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨化了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癒合了內心的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也有無法癒合的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間房子還是跟那個時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間在這裡停住了腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實伸他……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸夫怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子浴 很香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用這麼擔心我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾也已經準備好了 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是如今 我也有很多話想說給你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在這間房子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到的卻儘是回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然屋裡就能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要喬裝打扮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:07:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 八公呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼還不來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是巧不准她來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他不是那種會為了看煙花這種小事囉嗦的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有聯繫就是沒事的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不祥的證明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這次爽約
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就成了真正的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 無法停止流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為見面說清楚 就能夠釋懷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今才明白 在章司身邊的那段時光才是最開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司在成為我的戀人以前就已經是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拋棄內心的芥蒂 彷彿就可以回到從前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而真的是永遠失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就該好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（真）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算現在見到伸 也無法冷靜地談話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為寂寞 又會向他哭訴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有前科的人要自重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:09:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不想又一句話不說地背叛大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去的話 就應該說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 八公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jackson的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 快來吧 煙花已經開始放了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕見到伸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸夫他沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 那傢伙也很倔強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說不願意走入絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（的確如此）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（的確如此）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒用的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你不用在意他 趕快來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真和泰也很期待見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼掃興 現在才說不來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想快點見到你啊 八公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡 伸夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都已經說不想見到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還留在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒有這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是說怕見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八果然還是很愛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是你一廂情願的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 我瞭解的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕見了面又會迷失的那種恐懼 我最瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和巧的婚禮是在兩個星期以後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在又和你舊情複燃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就真的陷入泥沼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她當然會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 那就更不應該見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不願意和她一起陷入嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:12:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你一直以來只是同情被前男友拋棄 又被巧玩弄的小八而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那根本不能算喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是喜歡她的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你現在喜歡的是隔壁的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她和我有一樣的病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃藥就無法工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此她還是很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從前就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡幫助陷入困境的女孩 就算她和自己完全無關
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是想充英雄嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜 別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而一旦發覺自己有可能被牽連進去的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸 她只是在挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是輕鬆的愛情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜真是殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意這樣做 想讓他們陷入泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出那種話伸當然會認真起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八會比現在更痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸是和平主義者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他希望大家每天過著幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以努力想選擇一條可以得到最好結果的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不認為避免爭鬥是一件輕鬆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和自己的欲望抗爭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 要幾份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算逞強 我也要讓你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想快點見到你啊 八公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在跟你舊情複燃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八就會陷入泥沼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有看放煙花了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次吃路邊攤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是筷子很難用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會有提供叉子的店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要寵壞他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他練習一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然拉我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假髮會掉下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小八）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假髮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經到了門口 但是沒人開門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非大家都先去看煙花了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是房間裡還亮著燈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家等不及就先出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才應該道歉 遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在哪裡看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到你們我再打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？女裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不原意和她一起陷入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是輕鬆的愛情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？真？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 大家都在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 真又學美里說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的鑽石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚禮不請伸就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我都不請呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰和真都請了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會唱朋克版的瓢蟲桑巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？是什麼樣的歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會買CD給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你重新編曲 用吉他演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸為了讓你得到幸福 才選擇退出的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不幸福 他的犧牲就白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過巧的話 一定會讓你哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你這麼笨 愛上這種人 真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會因為他的一兩次婚外戀就受不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以揍他揍到氣消為止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 河邊擠滿了人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有看到章司和他的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為一切都落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在彷彿稍一側目就會被衝散的人潮之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想拉住娜娜的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那與伸有著相同體溫的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若真的天真爛漫地拉住她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會讓她覺得我反應遲鈍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過指間的風 感覺格外地冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天早已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花好看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要努力工作咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜比任何人都期望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻無法挽回的那個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直等待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20年也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50年也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜

